                            <comment id="12468736" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Tue, 30 Jan 2007 18:38:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;OK, I&apos;ve committed this.  I wanted to get it out of the way since it touched a number of files in a minor way (keeps other patches from applying cleanly).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;json.nl=flat default is subjective... if people think a different default is better, let&apos;s discuss now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
